body:
Captain Marvel - Avengers Endgame theories!!!

Okay so I JUST watched Captain marvel for the second time and this is what I noticed:

When Carol changes the colour of her suit with Monica, she tries different colours at first BUT those represent other heroes??

She tries Red-Gold at first, that’s clearly Iron man.

Second is Green-Gold which is Loki.

Third one was the rainbow which stands for the Bifrost.

And the last one was Green-Silver, Hulks colours!!

COINCIDENCE?? I THINK NOT!!!!

so like the rumors about Endgame are already similar, Tony is a major thing, Loki is not dead and Hulk is .. refusing to come back.

Talk to me guys.

title: New Avengers: Endgame Chinese Poster
body:
New #AvengersEndgame Chinese Poster

A piece of the official Chinese poster art for Avengers: Endgame has been revealed, and the artwork included is slightly different than what we have in the US.

Everyone except Black Widow is in a different pose, and it includes the Hulkbuster. You also get a much better look at Rocket in his comic-accurate costume and if you look very closely at Tony’s shoulder it looks like there’s more gold…

body:
Two New #AvengersEndgame TV Spots Released

In addition to the “Honor” spot Marvel released yesterday, the studio has aired two more TV spots for Avengers: Endgame during college basketball games last night.

While the second has absolutely no new footage we haven’t seen yet, the first does have a very brief new shot of Cap in that support group with new dialog talking about how “the world is in our hands”.

Those desperate for new footage…
